{"id": "vas_voice_001", "topic": "Caller Tune Service", "content": "LankaTel Caller Tune (Ring Back Tone): Replace boring ring tone with your favorite songs. Subscription: LKR 30/month + LKR 5/song. Activate via *123# or LankaTel app. Over 10,000 songs available in Sinhala, Tamil, English, and Hindi. Gift tunes to friends for LKR 10.", "category_type": "voice", "tags": ["vas", "caller-tune", "entertainment"]}
{"id": "vas_voice_002", "topic": "Call Forwarding Service", "content": "LankaTel Call Forwarding: Never miss important calls. Types: Always Forward (*21*number#), Busy Forward (*67*number#), No Answer Forward (*61*number#), Unreachable Forward (*62*number#). Deactivate with #21#, #67#, #61#, #62#. Standard call rates apply for forwarded calls.", "category_type": "voice", "tags": ["vas", "call-forwarding"]}
{"id": "vas_voice_003", "topic": "Conference Calling", "content": "LankaTel Conference Call: Connect up to 5 participants in a single call. Initiate: During call, press 'Add Call', dial second number, then 'Merge'. Each participant charged standard rates. Premium conference service (up to 20 participants) available for business accounts.", "category_type": "voice", "tags": ["vas", "conference", "business"]}
{"id": "vas_sms_001", "topic": "SMS Banking Alerts", "content": "LankaTel SMS Banking Service: Receive instant bank alerts via SMS. Partner banks: Commercial Bank, Sampath Bank, HNB, BOC, People's Bank, NDB. Setup through your bank's internet banking or mobile app. LankaTel provides free delivery - charges may apply from bank.", "category_type": "sms", "tags": ["vas", "sms", "banking"]}
{"id": "special_001", "topic": "Emergency Services Calling", "content": "Emergency calls from LankaTel are always free: Police (119), Ambulance/Fire (110), Accident Service (011-2691111), Government Info (1919), Women's Helpline (1938), Child Protection (1929). Emergency calls work even with zero balance or without a package. Location automatically shared with emergency services.", "category_type": "voice", "tags": ["emergency", "free", "safety"]}
